<h1 style="font-size:35px; text-align:center;">伪下拉组件MaskSelect</h1>
<br/>
<ul>
    <li>1、美化下拉样式，统一所有浏览器。</li>
    <li>2、解决层在部分浏览器中无法遮盖原生select问题。</li>
</ul>

<p>示例：</p>
原生select：<select name="test">
    <option value="a">a</option>
    <option value="b">b</option>
    <optgroup data-type="line"></optgroup>
    <optgroup label="ga">
        <option value="ga1">ga1</option>
        <option value="ga2">ga2</option>
    </optgroup>
    <option value="c">c</option>
    <option value="d">d</option>
    <optgroup label="gb">
        <option value="gb1">gb1</option>
        <option value="gb2">gb2</option>
    </optgroup>
</select>
美化后：
<div class="choice fake-select"  style="width:115px; margin-left:10px;" id="demo" data-trigger="mouseover">
    <select name="test" style="display:none;">
        <option value="a">a</option>
        <option value="b">b</option>
        <optgroup data-type="line"></optgroup>
        <optgroup label="ga">
            <option value="ga1">ga1</option>
            <option value="ga2">ga2</option>
        </optgroup>
        <option value="c">c</option>
        <option value="d">d</option>
        <optgroup label="gb">
            <option value="gb1">gb1</option>
            <option value="gb2">gb2</option>
        </optgroup>
    </select>
    <div class="choice-hd"><span></span> <div class="choice-button"><i class="icon">&#xf0d7;</i></div> </div>
    <dl class="choice-list" style="z-index:20;"></dl>
</div>
<p>HTML代码：</p>
<pre  class="brush: xhtml;">
<div class="choice fake-select"  style="width:115px; margin-left:10px;" id="demo" data-trigger="mouseover">
    <select name="test" style="display:none;">
        <option value="a">a</option>
        <option value="b">b</option>
        <optgroup data-type="line"></optgroup>
        <optgroup label="ga">
            <option value="ga1">ga1</option>
            <option value="ga2">ga2</option>
        </optgroup>
        <option value="c">c</option>
        <option value="d">d</option>
        <optgroup label="gb">
            <option value="gb1">gb1</option>
            <option value="gb2">gb2</option>
        </optgroup>
    </select>
    <div class="choice-hd"><span>Select module</span> <div class="choice-button"><i class="icon">&#xf0d7;</i></div> </div>
    <dl class="choice-list">
        <dd class="choice-option"><a href="#" >China</a></dd>
        <dd class="choice-option"><a href="#" >China Hongkong hello</a></dd>
        <dd class="choice-line"></dd>
        <dd class="choice-option"><a href="#" >China</a></dd>
    </dl>
</div>
</pre>
<p>PS:注意示例中的 <strong>data-trigger、data-type</strong></p>

<p>javascript调用：</p>
<pre class="brush: js;">
    new MaskSelect({
        carrier : document.getElementById('demo')
    })
</pre>

